      Subclasses of ExprNode in operations 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  EqOperation
      EqOperation class is a type of node that represents equality of name or value.
      class  GenericOperation
      GenericOperation class is an abstract class that contains the reference value or the reference name of the OperationNode, depending on the type of node (eq, ne node for name or le, lt, ge, gt, eq, ne node for value).
      class  GeOperation
      GeOperation class is a type of node that represents greater or equals to value.
      class  GtOperation
      GtOperation class is a type of node that represents greater than value.
      class  LeOperation
      LeOperation class is a type of node that represents less of equals to value.
      class  LtOperation
      LtOperation class is a type of node that represents less than value.
      class  NeOperation
      NeOperation class is a type of node that represents not equality of name or value.
